<comment id="5161989" author="spilli" created="Thu, 18 Sep 2025 07:42:22 -0700"><p><a href="https://jira.storage.hpecorp.net/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=arend.lensen%40hpe.com" class="user-hover" rel="arend.lensen@hpe.com">Arend Lensen</a><br/> Thanks for the update.</p> <p>as per initial comments from customer, if they run backups for shorter period (~one week or less) it use to run fine, that's the reason we mentioned as workaround available.</p> <p>But dev team got few points in their testing and they are actively working on it. We will keep you updated with the progress.</p> <p>Regards,<br/> Krishna.</p></comment>
